data.description: Enjoy country living on almost 8 acres with easy access to Chelsea, Harpersville, Childersburg and Sylacauga. Custom built 5 bedroom 4 full bath home built in 2021. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout with 9 foot ceilings. Large kitchen, oversized island, granite countertops, ceramic tile backsplash and black stainless appliances with black stainless farmhouse sink. Walk in pantry with custom shelving. Gas fireplace in living room with custom built-ins. Separate dining room. Two gas tankless hot water systems. Master has large walk-in closet and large bathroom. Marble shower and double sink. Tile flooring in bathrooms and laundry room. Upstairs bedroom/bonus room with bathroom and its own HVAC system. Attached carport. Newly installed porch railings.
